ergy, commonly found in metals such as brass, chrome, bronze etc</p><p>Armed with this basic understanding, watch the video below to see how to mimic those two main types of materials in RenderMan</p><p /><iframe allowfullscreen=\"\" allowtransparency=\"true\" class=\"fullscreen-video-iframe conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"false\" data-layout=\"default\" data-local-id=\"7ee04424-df48-4d10-8003-ffa60144230a\" data-macro-id=\"03a5da30ca3192d3ae7f3941d7384b24ee6eb91fde8fb0eb030ad6cd4b8bdde4\" data-macro-name=\"widget\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"540\" mozallowfullscreen=\"\" src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/471506695\" style=\"border:none; margin:1em 0em;\" webkitallowfullscreen=\"\" width=\"960\">\n</iframe>\n"
